{
  "_about": "Real OpenClaw Gateway frame shapes, extracted from the battle-tested Open WebUI pipe test suite (openclaw-notes/open-webui/openclaw_gateway_pipe_test.py) and production frame probes (HANDOFF-OPENWEBUI-2026-05-17.md). Each scenario protects a regression the bridge has hit before. Media paths use the real /home/node/.openclaw/media/outbound/ shape so the sanitizer exercises real conversion. sessionKey is the bridge 'webchat' namespace. These fixtures are replayed by tests/test_normalizer.py; do not edit shapes without a matching test update.",
